               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the second half of the year (fols.
                     3ra-173vb) &#xD; I-1) Maggābit (fols. 3ra-31vc)&#xD; I-2) Miyāzyā (fols.
                     32ra-53rc)&#xD; I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 54ra-81rc)&#xD; I-4) Sane (fols.
                     81va-108vc)&#xD; I-5) Ḥamle (fols. 109ra-144rc l.39) &#xD; I-6) Naḥāse” (fols.
                     144va–169rb l.2) &#xD; I-7) Ṗagʷǝmen (fols. 169rb l.3–173vb)&#xD; The
                     commemorative notices are followed by a ʿarke-hymns.</summary>
                  
